		<div class="inner greyBox">
			<h2 class="major special">Paper Review</h2>
			<p>Sign up to get your paper reviewed, or become a reviewer</p>
			<ul class="actions special stacked">
				<li><a href="/signup" class="button primary large">Sign Up</a></li>
				<li><a href="#two" class="button large scrolly">Learn more</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
