<!-- Two -->
	<section id="two" class="wrapper alt style2">
		<section class="spotlight">
			<div class="image"><img src="images/author.jpg" alt="" /></div>
			<div class="content">
				<h3 class="major">Authors</h3>
				<p>As an author you can upload your paper and pay to get it reviewed by one of the reviewers on this site.  You'll be notified when a reviewer has choosen to review your paper and get feedback on it when they're done.</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="spotlight">
			<div class="image"><img src="images/reviewer.jpg" alt="" /></div>
			<div class="content">
				<h3 class="major">Reviewers</h3>
				<p>As a verfied reviewer you'll review papers in your field of experise and get paid for doing so.  User selected email notifications come in when there's a paper that fits your criteria and you'll have the option to select which papers you want to get review and get paid for.</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="spotlight">
			<div class="image"><img src="images/payment.jpg" alt="" /></div>
			<div class="content">
				<h3 class="major">Payment</h3>
				<p>Authors pay for reviews when they send papers out for reviews.  Reviewers receieve payment after they have successfully reviewed a paper.</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</section>

